  "firstAcquaintance": "Demon Oru Baid is a young demon noble whose every gesture exudes aristocratic elegance.",
  "personality": "Impeccably courteous while giving off a special sense of warmth, willing to converse amicably with anyone regardless of their status.",
  "like": "Ketchup, afternoon tea",
  "familiarData": "Looks a lot like the human princess?\nThis is no coincidence -- she IS the kingdom princess Oru Baid, disguised as a demon for certain reasons.\n\nWith fake wings and a demon tail attached, dressed in demon formal wear, Her Highness transforms into a picture-perfect beautiful demon lady. Because her every gesture displays proper etiquette, she has become a role model for many young female demons to imitate.\nAs a member of the royal family, learning the art of disguise was a given. No one would imagine that this elegant demon lady is actually the human princess in disguise. Whether it is her tail or demon wings, she can use them fluently without any flaws.\n\n\"How is your tail more nimble than your hands?\"\n\"Hehe, it's a lady's skill.\"\n\nToday, Her Highness's disguise remains flawless. However, perhaps because she imitates demons a little too well, she has become more mischievous compared to her usual self, occasionally using her tail to play small pranks.",
